---
import Layout from '../layouts/Post.astro';

const originalDate : Date = new Date(import.meta.env.BUILD_DATE);
const formattedDate : string = originalDate.toLocaleString('fr-FR', {
	day: '2-digit',
	month: '2-digit',
	year: 'numeric',
	hour: '2-digit',
	minute: '2-digit',
});

---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="More information about me."
	pubDate={new Date('September 25 2023')}
	heroImage=""
>
	<h4>My Academic Journey</h4>
	<p>After completing my baccalauréat, I embarked on a journey of academic growth and specialization in the field of computer science and information technology.</p>

	<h5>BTS Systèmes Numériques</h5>
	<p>I pursued a <em>BTS Systèmes Numériques</em>, a two-year program that provided me with a strong foundation in digital technologies, including electronics, computer science, and telecommunications.</p>

	<h5>Licence Profession Métier de l'Informatique Application Web</h5>
	<p>Building on my BTS, I enrolled in a Bachelor's degree program with a professional focus on web application development. This program equipped me with the skills and knowledge necessary for web development, including languages, frameworks, and best practices.</p>

	<h5>Master Informatique</h5>
	<p>I am currently pursuing a Master's degree in computer science. This advanced program will further refine my expertise in the field and prepare me for a rewarding career in computer science, encompassing areas such as software development, data analysis, and artificial intelligence.</p>

	<h4>Server Information</h4>

	<p>This website is hosted on <a href='https://pulseheberg.com'>pulseheberg</a>,
		and the last successful update date was at {formattedDate}.
	</p>
</Layout>
